{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Requires SWS and js_ReaScriptAPI extensions\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 1)\tx360\tab If envelope for last touched Track FX parameter does not exist it is created.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 2)\tx360\tab Displays envelope in lane and scrolled into view/top of TCP.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 3)\tx360\tab Selects the envelope.\sa180\par}
}

