{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b 6 scripts to navigate FX presets / automate FX presets change + 1 auxiliary script.} {\b All complete with instructions.} BuyOne_Cycle through focused FX presets forward (guide inside).lua\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 BuyOne_Cycle through focused FX presets backwards (guide inside).lua\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 BuyOne_Dedicated FX presets forward switcher (FX ID dependent) (guide inside).lua\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 BuyOne_Dedicated FX presets backwards switcher (FX ID dependent) (guide inside).lua\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 BuyOne_Dedicated FX presets forward switcher (TAG dependent) (guide inside).lua\par}
