{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Splits selected MIDI item at every note or chord start.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 To be run from Arrange. The notes must not overlap, or they will be corrected if confirmed by the user. If declined the script won't run.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Supports both melodic and harmony parts. The length is only preserved for notes and chords which don't overlap notes/chords which follow them.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Chord notes whose start times differ will be treated as overlapping notes and chord structure won't be preserved if notes correction is applied.\par}
