{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 DESCRIPTION\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This script allows easy comping of items that were recorded in free item positioning mode.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 It activates (unmutes) the item under mouse and mutes overlapping items on the same track.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Items that only overlap slightly, due to crossfades, will not be muted. (The maximum allowed overlap can be edited in the script.)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 The script can be linked to a left-click mouse modifier in the "Media item" or "Media item bottom half" contexts.\par}
}

{\rtf1\ansi\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0 \fswiss Helvetica;}{\f1 Courier;}}
