{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs28 Tempo Marker List\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Displays a list of tempo markers.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Marker: Index in list.\line Time: On timeline.\line Meter: Time signature if set.\line BPM: Tempo at time.\line Bar: Bar set at time.\line Beat: Beat count at time.\line Linear: Set if gradual change.\par}
