{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Returns the average, median and statistical mode of all note velocities in current take (open ME window or selected item in Arrange). You can choose one of them to set as a threshold (or set your own value) and compress/expand differently the notes that their velocities are above the threshold, and those that are below. Values 1 to 100 bring note velocities towards the threshold (compress) and values -1 to -100 move them away (expand).\par}
