{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Works for the last clicked CC lane if several are open.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 If next/previous active CC envelope is already open in another visible lane, in the active lane it's skipped.\par}
