{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Also supports Pitch bend, Channel pressure and Program change envelopes.\line Ignores Velocity, Off Velocity, Text events, Notation enents and SySex lanes.\line CC00-31 14 bit CC lanes currently aren't supported either.\par}
