{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 INSTRUCTIONS\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 CC lanes can be selected by clicking with the mouse, or by using these shortcuts for commonly used CC types:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \f1 v = Velocity\line
