{\rtf1\ansi\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0 \fswiss Helvetica;}{\f1 Courier;}}
{\colortbl;\red255\green0\blue0;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\widowctrl\hyphauto

{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 ReaLauncher\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 A custom version of the startup prompt window for loading (recent) projects, project/track templates and more. With a bunch of additional features.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Uses 'Lokasenna's GUI library v2 for Lua' as base: https://forum.cockos.com/showthread.php?t=177772. Big thanks to Lokasenna for his work!!\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs32 Main features\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Separate tabs for [Recent Projects], (.rpp) [Project Templates], (.rtracktemplate) [Track Templates], (.rpp) [Projects], (.rpl) [Project Lists], (.rpp-bak) [Backups] and (.pdf) [Docs]\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Option to set custom folder paths for [Project Templates] and [Track Templates] - which are scanned in addition to the default template folder locations\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Option to set custom folder paths for the [Projects], [Project Lists], [Backups] and [Docs] tabs\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab List filter in each tab that supports the use of multiple search words separated by a 'space' character\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab File paths can be shown/hidden and also displayed optionally in the status bar\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Sorting options\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab [Favorites] tab to list and manage bookmarked favorites of each tab\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab [Follow Actions] tab to set Actions that are triggered after certain operations (New Tab, Load Project, etc.)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Global functions accessible via main button panel or context menu: [Open Project], [New Project], [New Tab], [Load in Tab], [Load] and [Insert]\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Selection and loading of multiple entries at once (multi-select via mouse is already part of Lokasenna's GUI library)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab 'Keep open' checkbox to toggle the automatic window closing behavior after Load/New/Insert operations\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Different tab selector styles (Tabstrip or Dropdown)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Scalable and resizeable window\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Customizable colors\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs32 Features that require SWS Extensions (2.9.8 or higher):\par}
