{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Get the group association bitfield for the VCA Leader which gets you a 32-bit integer. Each bit represents one of the 32 possible groups. A secondary function checks the next 32 groups.\par}
