{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Select the tracks where those bitfields match\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Show only selected tracks and hide all others\sa180\par}
