{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Except a few edge cases, now your new track will behave like it's actually hosting the instrument! You can put effects on it, create sends, etc. One limitation: you cannot folder these new tracks beneath the multi-instrument track due to the way feedback works in Reaper.\par}
