{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 Random track order for selected tracks by Will Develop\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs32 INFO:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab ReaScript Name: Random track order for selected tracks\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Author: Will Develop\par}
