{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 Simple Project Reconform\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 The script is under development, but you can try to use it. Read more: https://forum.cockos.com/showthread.php?t=288069\par}
