{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 5 scripts to toggle docked toolbars on mouse hover, meant to free up screen real estate when toolbars are not in active use:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 BuyOne_Cursor toggleable sidebars (settings inside).lua\par}
