{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 command+, - decrement chord type\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 command+. - increment chord type\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 command+shift+, - decrement chord inversion\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 command+shift+. - increment chord inversion\par}
