{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 Color tool with customizable color gradient palette and a user palette.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Use it to set custom Tracks / Items / Takes / Takes Markers / Markers / Regions colors.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://forum.cockos.com/showthread.php?t=252219"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
Thread in Cockos forum
}}}
\par}
{\pard \qc \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Requirement :\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab ReaImGui: ReaScript binding for Dear ImGui\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab js_ReaScriptAPI: API functions for ReaScripts\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.sws-extension.org"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
SWS Extension
}}}
\sa180\par}
{\pard \qc \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Features :\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Click on any color to set in selected Tracks/Items/Takes/Markers/Take Markers/Regions\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Target button automatically switch according to the last valid context\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Click on target button to fast switch inside each category\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Right-click on Target button manually choose to any target\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Click on Action button to start the displayed action\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Right-click on Action button to choose another action (Default / Random All / Random Each / In Order) :\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Right-click on "Settings" button to dock/undock (there is also a checkbox in the settings)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Drag any palette color and drop it in user color\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Drag and drop any user color to move it (or drop away to remove)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Right-click on user color to open popup menu (Edit / Get first selected target color / Paste Hex value / Remove / Clear all)\sa180\par}
{\pard \qc \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Mouse modifiers :\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Customize all mouse modifiers in Settings/Shortcuts menu\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab [Ctrl]/[Cmd] Insert new target with clicked color\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab [Ctrl+Alt]/[Cmd+Opt] Insert new named target with clicked color\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab [Shift+Ctrl]/[Opt] Check/Uncheck color\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab [Alt]/[Ctrl] Set color to children tracks too / to all takes (non active too)\sa180\par}
{\pard \qc \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Shortcuts :\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Keyboard shortcuts (see Settings/Shortcuts menu)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Arrows : Navigation - Go to next/previous element, depends on target\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab 1-9 numbers : Set user color by ID (works with modifiers also)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab 0 : Set default color (works with modifiers also)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Enter : Run action button (works with modifiers also)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab R : Run Random All (works with modifiers also)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab E : Run Random Each (works with modifiers also)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab I : Run In Order (works with modifiers also)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Backspace / Delete : Remove user color under mouse cursor\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Ctrl+C : Copy hex color under mouse cursor in clipboard\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Ctrl+V : Paste hex color from clipboard under mouse cursor\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Spacebar : Check/Uncheck color under mouse cursor, only on "Check list" mode for Random / In Order\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab [Ctrl+S] / [Cmd+S] : Save as user colors\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab [Ctrl+O] / [Cmd+O] : Load user colors file\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab [A] : Switch to Arm mode\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Many settings...\sa180\par}
