{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 tompad_MusicMath is a reascript to get ms from bpm and Hz from pitch in a Reaperproject.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 When script window is opened, it takes the current bpm from Reaper and by choosing note buttons it convert bpm to ms.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 By clicking the resulting ms-text the script is copying the ms to the systems clipboard (for pasting in to delay f.ex)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Any comments on coding, requests, bugs etc is welcome! PM me (tompad) on Reaper Forum (https://forum.cockos.com/member.php?u=19103).\par}
}

